# ============================================================
# HFWastelandZ — Admin Configuration
# File: $profile:HFWastelandZ_admins.conf
# ============================================================
#
# Defines server administrators by Steam64 ID.
# Admins get elevated access: Game Master (Zeus) mode,
# future in-game admin panel, dev tools visibility.
#
# FORMAT:
#   ADMIN <Steam64ID>   — one admin per line
#
# Steam64 IDs are 17-digit numbers. Find yours at:
#   https://steamid.io/ or in your Steam profile URL
#
# BEHAVIOR:
#   No config file      → no admins, GM access denied for all
#   Empty config        → no admins, GM access denied for all
#   ADMIN entries       → listed players get GM/admin access
#
# PERMISSIONS (future — currently all admins are full access):
#   ADMIN <Steam64ID>           — full admin (GM, kick, ban, teleport, etc.)
#   MODERATOR <Steam64ID>       — limited (kick, mute — future feature)
#
# ============================================================

# --- ADMINS ---
# Add one ADMIN line per server administrator
# Example:
#   ADMIN 76561198012345678

# ADMIN 76561198012345678
# ADMIN 76561198087654321
